recommended.title: PLEASURE OF PAIN
recommended.description: A young lady gets married to the man of her dreams, only to discover a monstrous side to a man she thought she knew.

recommended.title: MY NAME IS KHADI
recommended.description: A mother is on the quest to heal her daughter's youthful exuberance, whilst battling with her out of control attitude the daughter decides to leave and live life by her own rules.

recommended.title: MY NAME IS TAYO
recommended.description: After applying for more than 200 jobs, Tayo is frustrated and decided to try something new but all didn't go as planned.

recommended.title: 72 Hours
recommended.description: Two women trade places for 72 hours, to find out who is better at being a wife. Watch now.

recommended.title: Behind The Curtain
recommended.description: A conscientious employee about to go on trial for murder glumly recounts to her lawyer the story of how her dream job turned into an ultimate nightmare.

recommended.title: Different Passion
recommended.description: A young beautiful lady decides to follow her passion of being a Hairstylist, but is discouraged by her sister who believes she could take the fast lane to make quick money. She soon realises her passion will pave way for her.

recommended.title: Lamine
recommended.description: Lamine is a beautiful young woman who has developed a resentment towards men because of past unpleasant relationships. She draws her friends into her game of teaching men the lessons of their lives, until she meets a detective whose assignment is to investigate her for murder. This detective falls hopelessly in love with her and chooses to stay by her side even after discovering that she is a murderer. But will Lamine change her ways for him?...
